'''Budeshti - बुदेश्ति''' ([[rumunikani ćhib|rumunikanes]]: ''Budeşti'') si ek [[foro]], opretele 30 km ko sudvesto katar e [[Bukureshti]], o [[sherutno foro]] la [[Rumuniya]]ko. Kathe biyandilyas o butjanglo romano [[bashavno]] [[Yon Voiku]].

Kahte jivisaren 9,702 manusha (2002). Palal o ginipen le manushengo katar o [[2002]]to [[bersh]], 78.95% sas [[rumun]]urya, 21.00% [[roma]] thai 0.04% aver [[sel]]. Andi Rumuniya, kana ekhe [[seloro|selores]] si les buteder sar 20% ando ek [[thanipen]], atunch si les chachimata (xakaya) te labyarel la kana varekon del duma le autoritetenge. Vi o them trebul te kerel shkole vi [[dromenge patrya]] pe kodoya chhib. Kadya, o Budeshti si o korkoro foro andar i Rumuniya kai roma si buteder sar 20% (mai si aver thanimata, pale numa [[gav]]a).

Vi o [[dharm]] (relijiya), 99.59% si [[ortodokso|ortodoksurya]], 0.28% [[pentikostalo|pentikostalurya]] thai 0.11% aver dharm.

